## Privacy Policy

_Last updated: July 7, 2026_

This policy explains what information is collected when you use this website
([dana.lol](https://www.dana.lol)) and **Tripbot**, the chat bot that runs in
the live chat of the A Dana Life livestream on Twitch and YouTube. It is
written in plain language because the honest summary is short: very little
information is collected, and none of it is sold.

### Who runs this

A Dana Life is operated by **A Dana Life, LLC**, a company owned by an
individual (Dana). Questions about this policy can be sent by email to
[danadotlol@gmail.com](mailto:danadotlol@gmail.com) or through the
<%= link_to 'contact page', '/contact' %>.

### What is collected

**This website.** The site is static and does not require an account. If you
choose to use the <%= link_to 'contact page', '/contact' %>, the name, email
address, and message you submit are sent so that your message can be read and
answered. The site's host (Cloudflare) processes standard server request data
(such as IP address and browser type) to serve pages and protect against abuse.

**Tripbot (Twitch & YouTube live chat).** When you type in the live chat of the
A Dana Life stream, Tripbot reads public chat messages so it can respond to
commands (for example `!location`, `!weather`, or `!guess`). The only
information it sees is what the platform makes public: your chat **display
name** and the **text of the message** you send. Tripbot does **not** access
your email address, private messages, watch history, subscriptions, or any
data that isn't part of the public live chat.

On Twitch, your public display name may be associated with stream features such
as the miles leaderboard. On YouTube, Tripbot does not store viewer identity or
per-user data — it reads a chat message, responds, and keeps nothing.

### How YouTube data is used

Tripbot uses **YouTube API Services** to read the live chat of the active
broadcast and to post replies back into that same chat. By interacting with
Tripbot on YouTube, you are also agreeing to the
[YouTube Terms of Service](https://www.youtube.com/t/terms). Information handled
through the YouTube API is governed by the
[Google Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy).

Tripbot's access to the YouTube channel is authorized by the channel owner, not
by individual viewers, so there is no per-viewer login to revoke. The channel
owner can revoke Tripbot's access at any time through the
[Google security settings](https://security.google.com/settings/security/permissions).

Public chat data read through the API is processed only in memory to generate a
real-time reply, and is then discarded. It is **not** stored, logged, profiled,
combined with data from other sources, sold, or used for advertising. It is
**not shared with any internal team or external third party**: the only place a
message goes is back to YouTube's own API when Tripbot posts its reply into the
same chat. A Dana Life, LLC is a single-operator company with no other internal
recipients of this data.

### What is not done

- Your information is **not sold** or rented to anyone.
- Information is **not used for advertising** or ad targeting.
- No attempt is made to identify viewers beyond their public chat display name.

### Data retention

Contact-form messages are kept only as long as needed to respond to them.
Public YouTube live-chat data is processed transiently and not stored. Twitch
chat activity that powers stream features (such as the leaderboard) is kept for
as long as those features run, and can be removed on request.

### Cookies and device storage

**This website.** The site does not use analytics, advertising, or tracking
cookies, and sets no first-party cookies of its own. The host (Cloudflare) may
place strictly-necessary cookies (such as `__cf_bm`) on your device to serve
pages and protect against abuse; these are described in the
[Cloudflare cookie policy](https://www.cloudflare.com/cookie-policy/). Nothing
on the site reads or writes any other cookies, `localStorage`, or similar
technology on your device or browser.

**Tripbot (YouTube live chat).** Tripbot runs server-side against the YouTube
API. It does **not** place, access, or recognize any cookies, identifiers, or
other storage on your device or browser.

### Third-party services

Using this site and stream necessarily involves a few service providers, each
with its own privacy policy:

- **Twitch** — [privacy policy](https://www.twitch.tv/p/legal/privacy-notice/)
- **YouTube / Google** — [privacy policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)
- **Cloudflare** (website hosting) — [privacy policy](https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/)

### Children

This site and stream are intended for a general audience and are not directed at
children under 13. No information is knowingly collected from children.

### Changes to this policy

This policy may be updated from time to time. Material changes will be reflected
in the "last updated" date at the top of this page.

### Contact

If you have any questions about privacy or want information removed, please get
in touch by email at [danadotlol@gmail.com](mailto:danadotlol@gmail.com) or
through the <%= link_to 'contact page', '/contact' %>.
